{"TopicId":211354,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Im new send help lol","CreatedByName":"AngryPolishMan","CreatedById":224610,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T00:54:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"AngryPolishMan","CreatedById":224610,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T00:54:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nive just gotten ksp cause its free on epic and ive wanted the game for years. i started a sience mode playthru and for some reason dont get sience from my launches at all. can anyone explain how sience actually works and how u get it consistently?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T01:11:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe game has a couple of modes. Science is not collected in all of them. Are you sure you selected the right kind of campaign?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, welcome to the game, and the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zozaf Kerman","CreatedById":219910,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T01:23:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a great guide that goes over the details of science in ksp, and should meet your needs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002257838\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3210611331\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/56973-understanding-science-points/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=846307\u0026amp;embedComment=846307\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-846307\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Director_Valle","CreatedById":224482,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T05:06:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Sj-POZ_y7Rk?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Collecting Science - KSP Beginner\u0027s Tutorial\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T11:26:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forums \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/224610-angrypolishman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022224610\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/224610-angrypolishman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@AngryPolishMan\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003EPerhaps\u003C/s\u003E As suggested above, the Science system is quite complex. I suggest that you first experiment in Sandbox mode to see how rockets, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, EVA etc. work before attempting a Science game, this way you\u0027ll know how things work and you\u0027ll then be able to focus more on the Science system.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mahnarch","CreatedById":114432,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-11T01:02:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216498\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211354\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673090788\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nazalassa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/7/2023 at 6:26 AM, Nazalassa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n~ I suggest that you first experiment in Sandbox mode ~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI remember way back in 2014 I thought I\u0027d start in Sandbox mode but, was overwhelmed by the number of parts available.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found it easier to start in Career and learn my way up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}